      "span_text": "A comparison of sequences showed a 100% identity with all available sequences of the Sumatran rhinoceros from GenBank with respect to the trimmed alignment and also with the untrimmed sequence of the Sumatran rhinoceros from the study of [CITATION_1] leaving no doubt on the correct molecular identification of the ZMH specimen."
